1. *Verujem* da će biti lepo vreme sutra. (I believe that the weather will be nice tomorrow.)
2. On *veruje* u ljubav na prvi pogled. (He believes in love at first sight.)
3. Ti *veruješ* u sebe, to je najvažnije. (You believe in yourself, that's the most important thing.)
4. Da li *veruješ* u boga? (Do you believe in God?)
5. *Verovanje* u zvezde može biti veoma zabavno. (Believing in stars can be very fun.)
6. Njen *verovalac* ju je došao posetiti. (Her believer came to visit her.)
7. *Verujem* da ćeš uspeti ako se potrudiš. (I believe that you will succeed if you try.)
8. Oni su *neverujući* prema novim tehnologijama. (They are skeptical towards new technologies.)
9. Njihova *neverica* u izjavu bila je jasna. (Their disbelief in the statement was clear.)
10. Tvoje *verovanje* u ovu ideju je neopravdano. (Your belief in this idea is unjustified.)